{"chapters": {"ch01-experiencia-no-campo": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A LOGOTERAPIA E A VONTADE DE SENTIDO</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">EM BUSCA</span> <span class=\"bd\">DE SENTIDO</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Viktor E. Frankl</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PRIMEIRA PARTE: A Experiência no Campo</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">As Três Fases do Prisioneiro</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><strong><span class=\"dc\">C</span>hoque</strong> (chegada): terror, frieza defensiva, humor mórbido e a 'ilusão do indulto'. <strong>Apatia</strong> (rotina): embotamento que protege e, no excesso, desumaniza. <strong>Despersonalização</strong> (libertação): tudo parece irreal; é preciso reaprender a sentir.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Como aplicar</div><div class=\"tipbody\">leia qualquer entrada abrupta numa situação extrema (diagnóstico, perda, exílio) por essas fases — cada uma pede uma resposta interior diferente.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PRIMEIRA PARTE: A Experiência no Campo</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Porquê e Como (Nietzsche)</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span> bússola do livro: <em>'quem tem um porquê para viver suporta quase qualquer como'</em>. No campo, a resistência vinha menos da força física e mais de haver um sentido, uma meta, alguém esperando — um <strong>porquê</strong>.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Modelo mental</div><div class=\"tipbody\">antes de perguntar 'como aguentar?', encontre o 'por que / para que aguentar'.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PRIMEIRA PARTE: A Experiência no Campo</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Amor, Beleza e Humor</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">P</span>rivado do mundo exterior, o homem aprofunda a <strong>vida interior</strong>. A imagem do ser amado sustenta o prisioneiro: salva-se o homem pelo e no amor. A <strong>beleza</strong> (um pôr do sol) e o <strong>humor</strong> (rir do horror) provam a alma viva.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Para refletir</div><div class=\"tipbody\">ama-se a essência do outro, presente ou não — o amor dá sentido independentemente da posse.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch02-a-ultima-liberdade-e-o-sofrimento": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A LOGOTERAPIA E A VONTADE DE SENTIDO</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">EM BUSCA</span> <span class=\"bd\">DE SENTIDO</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Viktor E. Frankl</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>A Última Liberdade e o Sentido do Sofrimento</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">A Inversão da Pergunta</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">N</span>ão cabe ao homem perguntar 'qual o sentido da vida?', mas <strong>responder à pergunta que a vida lhe faz</strong>. Somos os interrogados; respondemos agindo na tarefa concreta de cada momento — isso é <strong>responsabilidade</strong>.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Como aplicar</div><div class=\"tipbody\">reformule 'qual o sentido de tudo isto?' em 'o que esta situação, agora, me pede para fazer ou ser?'.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>A Última Liberdade e o Sentido do Sofrimento</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Sofrimento com Sentido</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">O</span> sofrimento <strong>evitável</strong> deve ser evitado (sofrer por sofrer é masoquismo). Mas o sofrimento <strong>inevitável</strong> carrega um sentido potencial: a atitude digna diante dele transforma a tragédia em conquista interior.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Regra</div><div class=\"tipbody\">mude o que pode mudar; dê sentido ao que não pode.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>A Última Liberdade e o Sentido do Sofrimento</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">O Sentido é Único e Concreto</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">O</span> sentido é <strong>descoberto, não inventado</strong> — detecta-se no mundo, fora de si. E é sempre <strong>concreto e único</strong>: muda de pessoa para pessoa e de hora para hora. Não há um 'sentido da vida' genérico.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Para refletir</div><div class=\"tipbody\">manter uma meta no futuro (uma tarefa, alguém) sustenta o homem no presente mais duro.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch03-conceitos-da-logoterapia": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A LOGOTERAPIA E A VONTADE DE SENTIDO</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">EM BUSCA</span> <span class=\"bd\">DE SENTIDO</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Viktor E. Frankl</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>SEGUNDA PARTE: Conceitos da Logoterapia</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">As Três Escolas Vienenses</h1><p class=\"ed-body\">1ª <strong>Freud</strong> → vontade de prazer. 2ª <strong>Adler</strong> → vontade de poder. 3ª <strong>Frankl</strong> → <strong>vontade de sentido</strong>. A logoterapia cura pela busca de sentido, voltada ao futuro a realizar.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Modelo mental</div><div class=\"tipbody\">o homem é <em>autotranscendente</em> — realiza-se ao esquecer-se de si numa causa ou em alguém, não girando em torno do próprio eu.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>SEGUNDA PARTE: Conceitos da Logoterapia</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Vazio Existencial</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span> frustração da vontade de sentido produz o sentimento de <strong>vazio, tédio e ausência de propósito</strong> — fenômeno de massa do nosso tempo. Manifesta-se no <strong>conformismo</strong> (fazer o que os outros fazem) e no <strong>totalitarismo</strong> (fazer o que mandam).</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Como aplicar</div><div class=\"tipbody\">leia o tédio crônico como sentido frustrado — pergunte o 'para quê', não só medique o humor.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>SEGUNDA PARTE: Conceitos da Logoterapia</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Neurose Noogênica · Tensão Sadia</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span> <strong>neurose noogênica</strong> nasce de conflitos existenciais/espirituais (de <em>noös</em>), não de pulsões — pede logoterapia. E a saúde não é equilíbrio sem tensão: é a <strong>tensão sadia</strong> rumo a uma meta digna. Homeostase plena = vazio.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Para refletir</div><div class=\"tipbody\">não precisamos de uma vida sem exigências, mas do esforço por uma meta que valha a pena.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch04-tecnicas-e-otimismo-tragico": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A LOGOTERAPIA E A VONTADE DE SENTIDO</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">EM BUSCA</span> <span class=\"bd\">DE SENTIDO</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Viktor E. Frankl</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">3</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>Técnicas e o Otimismo Trágico</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Intenção Paradoxal</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">C</span>ontra o medo que se autorrealiza (fobia, insônia): o paciente é convidado a <strong>desejar, com humor e exagero, justamente o que teme</strong> ('vou tentar suar o máximo possível'). O <strong>autodistanciamento</strong> e o riso cortam a ansiedade antecipatória.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Como aplicar</div><div class=\"tipbody\">ninguém consegue <em>querer</em> de propósito o sintoma com a mesma força com que o teme — o círculo se rompe.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>Técnicas e o Otimismo Trágico</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Dereflexão</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">C</span>ontra a <strong>hiperreflexão</strong> (auto-observação que sabota o desempenho): <strong>desviar a atenção de si</strong> para um sentido, uma tarefa ou outra pessoa. O que foge quando perseguido — sono, prazer, felicidade — volta quando deixa de ser alvo.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Regra</div><div class=\"tipbody\">felicidade não se persegue, ela sobrevém — como efeito de um sentido realizado.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>03</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">EM BUSCA DE SENTIDO</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>Técnicas e o Otimismo Trágico</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Otimismo Trágico</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">D</span>izer 'sim' à vida apesar da <strong>tríade trágica</strong> — dor, culpa e morte. Converter cada uma: <strong>dor</strong> em conquista; <strong>culpa</strong> em mudança para melhor; <strong>transitoriedade</strong> em responsabilidade de agir agora.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Para refletir</div><div class=\"tipbody\">é otimismo <em>apesar</em> da tragédia, não em negação dela.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"]}}